<li id="cite_note-98"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-98">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1215172403"><cite class="citation web cs1"><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://web.archive.org/web/20041217072309/http://www.ccarnet.org/cgi-bin/respdisp.pl?file=8&amp;year=5756">"CCARnet.org"</a>. Archived from <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.ccarnet.org/cgi-bin/respdisp.pl?file=8&amp;year=5756">the original</a> on December 17, 2004.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.btitle=CCARnet.org&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ccarnet.org%2Fcgi-bin%2Frespdisp.pl%3Ffile%3D8%26year%3D5756&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AJewish+views+on+marriage" class="Z3988"></span></span>
</li>
</ol></div></div>
